(firstQuint)Clinical Trail of Tang-min-Ling Pills in Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus.

 Type 2 diabetes mellitus combined liver-stomach heat retension syndrome were recruited, which were divided into 3 groups .

The patients were randomly taken with high-dosage (12g Tang-min-ling pills every time), low-dosage (6g Tang-min-ling pills every time), placebo by 3 times every day for 12 weeks.

